entries.title: Deliver Jabba's Gifts to Imperial VIP's (final)
entries.split_quest_alert: Some high-level Imperials are coming to visit the prison... and they could use escort. More details to come...
entries.hello_p: Good to see you, pilot! I have your delivery ready for transfer.
entries.hello_d: This is highly irregular, pilot! What are we doing here?
entries.found_loc_p: Fly to this location and meet our transport.
entries.found_loc_d: Got an update for you... follow this waypoint. Meet up with the Imperial Inquisitor.
entries.docking_started_pickup: Hey there! We've got...something... for the Imperial Inquisitor.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: There you go! That should be the last delivery for today, my friend.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: You tell Jabba the Hutt that the Imperial Inquisitors do not take bribes! Begone!
entries.attack_notify: Enemy craft detected on attack vector.
entries.arrived_at_pickup: Your delivery target (an Imperial Inquisitor) should be here very soon...
entries.arrived_at_delivery: The transport should be here shortly...
